    - rid: 5422255992042160578
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hello. Are you Meredith? I came about the contract you posted on the
          board. Is it available?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160579
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Hello, how are you today?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160580
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Yes, I still need someone to find my husband. He got lost in the forest.
          Can you find him?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160581
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Where did he go?
    - rid: 5422255992042160582
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: What does he look like?
    - rid: 5422255992042160583
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: No problem, i will find him.
    - rid: 5422255992042160584
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He left through the south gate, you can ask the guards where he went.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160585
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He was last wearing a red jacket and a white cap. His name is Jovan.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160586
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you my dear. There is a reward when you find him. Come back with
          him please.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160587
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: It's very bad, my husband hasn't come home since yesterday. He went
          out into the forest. I'm afraid the wolves got to him.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160588
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I can look for him.
    - rid: 5422255992042160589
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: "\rI'm sorry, I hope he'll be found."
    - rid: 5422255992042160590
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Oh my god, I think Erel himself sent you to me. Do you need any information?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160591
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Did you find him?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160592
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! I prayed to Alyss, hoping she would
          send me someone to help, and you appeared. Here's reward. May Alyss and
          Erel take care of you.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160593
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Not yet, I am still looking for him.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160594
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, I am waiting for news.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160595
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You won't go into the forest alone anymore.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160596
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160597
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422255992042160598
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: What a beautiful day!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160599
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You know I have to because it's my job.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422255992042160600
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: You will find another one.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
--- !u!114 &7128122449418335031
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e5800231a05eaae43b00503881229245, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  originalLanguage: en
  translationSets:
  - counter: 25
    languageCode: en
    translations:
    - id: 0
      language: en
      text: Player
    - id: 1
      language: en
      text: Hello. Are you Meredith? I came about the contract you posted on the
        board. Is it available?
    - id: 2
      language: en
      text: Hello, how are you today?
    - id: 3
      language: en
      text: Meredith
    - id: 4
      language: en
      text: Yes, I still need someone to find my husband. He got lost in the forest.
        Can you find him?
    - id: 5
      language: en
      text: Where did he go?
    - id: 6
      language: en
      text: What does he look like?
    - id: 7
      language: en
      text: No problem, i will find him.
    - id: 8
      language: en
      text: He left through the south gate, you can ask the guards where he went.
    - id: 9
      language: en
      text: He was last wearing a red jacket and a white cap. His name is Jovan.
    - id: 10
      language: en
      text: Thank you my dear. There is a reward when you find him. Come back with
        him please.
    - id: 11
      language: en
      text: It's very bad, my husband hasn't come home since yesterday. He went out
        into the forest. I'm afraid the wolves got to him.
    - id: 12
      language: en
      text: I can look for him.
    - id: 13
      language: en
      text: "\rI'm sorry, I hope he'll be found."
    - id: 14
      language: en
      text: Oh my god, I think Erel himself sent you to me Do you need any information?
    - id: 15
      language: en
      text: Oh my god, I think Erel himself sent you to me. Do you need any information?
    - id: 16
      language: en
      text: Did you find him?
    - id: 17
      language: en
      text: Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! I prayed to Alyss, hoping she would
        send me someone to help, and you appeared. Here's reward. May Alyss and Erel
        take care of you.
    - id: 18
      language: en
      text: Not yet, I am still looking for him.
    - id: 19
      language: en
      text: Okay, I am waiting for news.
    - id: 20
      language: en
      text: You won't go into the forest alone anymore.
    - id: 21
      language: en
      text: Jovan
    - id: 22
      language: en
      text: What a beautiful day!
    - id: 23
      language: en
      text: You know I have to because it's my job.
    - id: 24
      language: en
      text: You will find another one.
